Reverse Integer

OPTIMAL::


class Solution {
    public int reverse(int x) {
         long reverse = 0;
        while (x != 0 ) {

            reverse = reverse * 10 + x % 10;
            x /= 10;
        }
       if(reverse >= Integer.MIN_VALUE && reverse <= Integer.MAX_VALUE)
            return (int)reverse; 
         else
             return 0; 
    }
}

Time Complexity: O(N)
Space Complexity: O(1)
